      <lg xml:id="TolE0389">
<l>aḷavu niṟaiyu meṇṇum varuvaḻi</l>
<l>neṭumutal kuṟukalu mukaram varutaluṅ</l>
<l>kaṭinilai yiṉṟē yāciri yaṟka</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>It is not against the opinion of scholars</l>
<l>that the initial long [vowel] is shortened and <foreign xml:lang="ta">u</foreign> is inserted</l>
<l>when measure, weight and number occur.<note
              place="foot">e.g. <foreign xml:lang="ta">eḻukalam, eḻupalam, eḻumūṉṟu</foreign> etc.</note></l>
      </lg>
    </div>
